<i>noun</i>: 적립 [정닙], 적금 [적끔], 저축 [저ː축], 저금 [저ː금] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>적립 [정닙]</dt><br>
<dd>raising; saving</dd><br>
<dd>돈이나 물건 등을 모아 둠.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saving money, items, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>적금 [적끔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. saving; savings</dd><br>
<dd>돈을 모음. 또는 그 돈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of accumulating money, or such money.</dd><br>
<dd>2. term deposit</dd><br>
<dd>은행에 일정한 돈을 일정한 기간 동안 낸 다음에 찾는 저금.</dd><br>
<dd>A type of savings where deposits are made with the bank over a certain period before withdrawal.</dd><br>
<dt>저축 [저ː축]</dt><br>
<dd>1. saving</dd><br>
<dd>돈이나 재물 등을 아껴 써서 모아 둠.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saving money, wealth, etc., by spending it frugally.</dd><br>
<dd>2. savings</dd><br>
<dd>벌어들인 돈 가운데 쓰지 않고 남은 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>Earned money that one has left after spending.</dd><br>
<dt>저금 [저ː금]</dt><br>
<dd>saving; savings</dd><br>
<dd>돈을 모아 두거나 은행 등의 금융 기관에 맡김. 또는 그런 돈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saving money or entrusting it to a financial institution like a bank, etc., or such money.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>